Author: bashytr0n
Text: This is me for sure. I still have fat arms at my lowest weight. I can mold my life around training and nutrition and fasting, miss out on social events, isolate myself, walk everywhere, basically lose the ability to feel true pleasure and at the end of the day its worth it only for the self punishment and not for the physical results which tbh are just "acceptable" but never enough.

Author: sstephenn
Text: Definitely relate. And then I’m like what’s the point I’ll never even look good at this low weight i have weird proportions ahhHhh trying to maintain but it’s difficult
